sql:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT patient_id) AS no_show_patient_count
FROM no_show_analysis
WHERE no_show_count > 0;

external_knowledge:
Active patients: patients who are currently active in the system (is_active = 1); 
Frequently missing appointments: no_show_percentage > 0.50; 
Recent no-show frequency: no_show_count_last_three_months (counts the number of no-show appointments for each patient over the last three months).
